<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include('../includes/head.ejs') %>
    <style>
      .about-page {
        position: relative;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdfa 0%, #eff6ff 50%, #fef2f2 100%);
        background-attachment: fixed;
        overflow-x: hidden;
        padding: 80px 0 0;
      }
      .about-background {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: 0;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 150%;
        height: 300px;
        border-top-left-radius: 50%;
        border-top-right-radius: 50%;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d9488, #0284c7, #3b82f6, #ef4444);
        z-index: 1;
        opacity: 0.9;
      }
      .about-content {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 10;
      }
      .text-teal {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d9488, #0284c7);
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        background-clip: text;
        font-weight: 800;
      }
      .quote-section {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #14b8a6, #0ea5e9, #3b82f6);
        color: white;
        border-radius: 2rem;
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        padding: 3rem !important;
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }
      .quote-section::before {
        content: '"';
        position: absolute;
        top: -20px;
        left: 20px;
        font-size: 150px;
        opacity: 0.1;
        font-family: Georgia, serif;
      }
      .team-card {
        background: white;
        border-radius: 1.5rem;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border: 3px solid transparent;
        background-clip: padding-box;
        width: 90%;
        max-width: 320px;
        margin: auto;
        transition: all 0.4s ease;
        position: relative;
      }
      .team-card::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: -3px;
        left: -3px;
        right: -3px;
        bottom: -3px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #14b8a6, #f97316, #ef4444, #3b82f6);
        border-radius: 1.5rem;
        z-index: -1;
        opacity: 0;
        transition: opacity 0.4s ease;
      }
      .team-card:hover::before {
        opacity: 1;
      }
      .team-card:hover {
        transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.03);
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(13, 148, 136, 0.25);
      }
      .team-card img {
        width: 160px;
        height: 160px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        border: 5px solid #5eead4;
        object-fit: contain;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdfa, #dbeafe);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
      }
      .team-card:hover img {
        transform: scale(1.1) rotate(-5deg);
        border-color: #f97316;
      }
      .instagram-section {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff, #f0fdfa);
        border-radius: 2rem;
        box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        border: 2px solid rgba(13, 148, 136, 0.1);
      }
      .btn-instagram {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f97316, #ef4444, #e91e63);
        color: white;
        font-weight: 700;
        border: none;
        padding: 0.9rem 2.5rem;
        border-radius: 9999px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.3);
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
        font-size: 1.05rem;
      }
      .btn-instagram:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.4);
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444, #e91e63, #f97316);
      }
      .carousel-item {
        transition: transform 0.6s ease-in-out;
      }
      .carousel-item img {
        border-radius: 2rem;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        border: 3px solid white;
      }
      @media (max-width: 767px) {
        #teamCarousel .carousel-control-prev,
        #teamCarousel .carousel-control-next {
          display: none;
        }
      }
      h1.display-4 {
        font-size: 3.5rem;
        font-weight: 800;
        letter-spacing: -1px;
      }
      h2.display-4 {
        font-size: 3rem;
        font-weight: 800;
      }
      h3.h2 {
        font-size: 2.2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.3;
      }
      .lead {
        font-size: 1.15rem;
        line-height: 1.8;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('../includes/tbcare/navbar-landing.ejs') %>

    <div class="about-page">
      <div class="about-background"></div>
      <div class="container about-content py-5">
        <section class="text-center py-5 my-5 wow fadeIn">
          <h1 class="display-4 font-weight-bold text-teal">About TBCare</h1>
          <p class="lead text-secondary mt-3 mx-auto" style="max-width: 800px">Project ini didanai oleh <b>Belmawa - Dikti - Kemendiktisaintek RI</b> dan digarap oleh tim <b>PKM-KC Institut Teknologi Sepuluh Nopember</b>.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="my-5 py-5">
          <div class="row align-items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 mb-lg-0 wow fadeInLeft">
              <h3 class="h2 font-weight-bold text-teal mb-4">Sistem Peringatan Dini Tuberkulosis Berdasarkan Suara Batuk</h3>
              <p class="text-secondary" style="font-size: 1.1rem"><b>TBCare</b> adalah sebuah sistem inovatif...<br /><br />Misi TBCare adalah... menciptakan masa depan Indonesia yang lebih sehat.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 wow fadeInRight">
              <div id="imageCarousel" class="carousel slide shadow-lg" data-ride="carousel">
                <div class="carousel-inner">
                  <div class="carousel-item active"><img src="/images/tbcare_landing/berita1.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="Berita 1" /></div>
                  <div class="carousel-item"><img src="/images/tbcare_landing/berita2.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="Berita 2" /></div>
                  <div class="carousel-item"><img src="/images/tbcare_landing/berita3.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="Berita 3" /></div>
                  <div class="carousel-item"><img src="/images/tbcare_landing/berita4.png" class="d-block w-100" alt="Berita 4" /></div>
                </div>
                <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#imageCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev"><span class="carousel-control-prev-icon"></span></a>
                <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#imageCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next"><span class="carousel-control-next-icon"></span></a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="my-5 py-5 wow fadeInUp">
          <div class="quote-section p-5 text-center">
            <h3 class="h2 font-weight-light">“Teknologi hadir bukan hanya untuk mempermudah, tapi juga untuk menyelamatkan nyawa. Bersama TBCare, mari wujudkan Indonesia bebas Tuberkulosis 2030.”</h3>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="my-5 py-5 text-center wow fadeIn">
          <h2 class="display-4 font-weight-bold text-teal mb-5">Our Team</h2>
          <div id="teamCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
            <div class="carousel-inner">
              <div class="carousel-item active">
                <div class="row">
                  <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <div class="team-card p-4">
                      <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/team/nathania.png" class="mx-auto" alt="Nathania" />
                      <h4 class="mt-3">Nathania</h4>
                      <p class="text-teal font-weight-bold">Project Manager</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-md-4 mb-4 d-none d-md-block">
                    <div class="team-card p-4">
                      <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/team/smiski.png" class="mx-auto" alt="Miskiyah" />
                      <h4 class="mt-3">Miskiyah</h4>
                      <p class="text-teal font-weight-bold">Website & Design</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-md-4 mb-4 d-none d-md-block">
                    <div class="team-card p-4">
                      <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/team/faisal.png" class="mx-auto" alt="Faisal" />
                      <h4 class="mt-3">Faisal</h4>
                      <p class="text-teal font-weight-bold">AI & Data</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="carousel-item">
                <div class="row justify-content-center">
                  <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
                    <div class="team-card p-4">
                      <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/team/rizki.png" class="mx-auto" alt="Rizki" />
                      <h4 class="mt-3">Rizki</h4>
                      <p class="text-teal font-weight-bold">Mobile App</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                  <div class="col-md-4 mb-4 d-none d-md-block">
                    <div class="team-card p-4">
                      <img src="/images/tbcare_landing/team/stanis.png" class="mx-auto" alt="Stanis" />
                      <h4 class="mt-3">Stanis</h4>
                      <p class="text-teal font-weight-bold">Hardware & IoT</p>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#teamCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev" style="width: auto; left: -50px"
              ><span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" style="background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); border-radius: 50%; padding: 20px"></span
            ></a>
            <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#teamCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next" style="width: auto; right: -50px"
              ><span class="carousel-control-next-icon" style="background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3); border-radius: 50%; padding: 20px"></span
            ></a>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="my-5 py-5 wow fadeInUp">
          <div class="instagram-section p-5">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
              <div class="col-md-6 text-center text-md-left mb-4 mb-md-0">
                <h3 class="display-4 font-weight-bold text-warning">Ikuti Perjalanan Kami!</h3>
                <p class="text-secondary my-4">Dapatkan informasi terbaru mengenai perkembangan TBCare, riset, dan berita seputar teknologi kesehatan langsung dari kami.</p>
                <a href="https://instagram.com/tbcare.its" target="_blank" class="btn btn-instagram rounded-pill px-5 py-3">Follow us on Instagram</a>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6"><img src="/images/tbcare_landing/ig.png" alt="Instagram Preview" class="img-fluid rounded shadow" /></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('../includes/tbcare/footer-landing.ejs') %> <%- include('../includes/end.ejs') %>
  </body>
</html>
